  "To become the world's most trusted and innovative travel accommodation platform, where every traveler finds their perfect stay and every host reaches their ideal guests. We envision a future where travel brings people together, fosters cultural understanding, and creates lasting memories.": "Har bir sayohatchi o'ziga mos turar joy topishi va har bir mezbonning ideal mehmonlarga yetishi mumkin bo'lgan, dunyodagi eng ishonchli va innovatsion sayohat platformasiga aylanish. Biz sayohat odamlarni birlashtirgan, madaniy tushunishni rivojlantirgan va abadiy xotiralar yaratgan kelajakni ko'ramiz.",
  "To empower travelers around the globe with the tools, choices, and confidence to discover and book their ideal accommodations. We strive to make travel accessible, affordable, and enjoyable for everyone, while supporting local hosts and communities.": "Butun dunyo bo'ylab sayohatchilarni ideal turar joylarini topish va bron qilish uchun zarur vositalar, tanlov imkoniyatlari va ishonch bilan ta'minlash. Mahalliy mezbonlar va jamoalarni qo'llab-quvvatlagan holda, sayohatni hammaga qulay, arzon va zavqli qilishga intilamiz.",
